OL,3,CInside the club which helped send Rory
OL,4,Con path to greatness
OL,6,FThere's nothing quite like the hustle
OL,7,Fand bustle of a golf club on the final
OL,8,Fnight of the Masters.
OL,10,FHowever when it's Rory McIlroy's
OL,11,Fhometown club, it's even more special.
OL,12,FSupporters were preparing for another
OL,13,Fnight of drama. Oh, how it delivered.
OL,15,FAs the sun set on Northern Ireland's
OL,16,FHolywood hills, excitement and
OL,17,Fexpectation filled the air alongside
OL,18,Fthe clinking of pint glasses and
OL,19,Fmurmurings of 'here we go again'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776272751
OL,3,CInside the club which helped send Rory
OL,4,Con path to greatness
OL,6,FThat was until their hero stepped onto
OL,7,Fthe first tee.
OL,9,FYou could cut the silence with a knife
OL,10,Fas he prepared to hit the opening shot
OL,11,Fon day four at Augusta on a day when
OL,12,Fhistory could be made again.
OL,14,FFrom the club captain sparking up
OL,15,Fconversation with revellers to
OL,16,Fchildren colouring in 'Let's go Rory'
OL,17,Fsigns, all hoped he could retain that
OL,18,Ffamous green jacket.
OL,20,FNerves were present from the start.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776272751
OL,3,CInside the club which helped send Rory
OL,4,Con path to greatness
OL,6,FAnd no wonder. Four holes in, McIlroy
OL,7,Fhit a double bogey, preceded by two
OL,8,Fpars and a birdie.
OL,10,FBut he bounced back with another
OL,11,Fbirdie on the fifth.
OL,13,FHowever the biggest cheer of the front
OL,14,Fnine came at the 7th - a birdie putt
OL,15,Fthat sent supporters wild with as much
OL,16,Frelief as happiness.
OL,18,FThen on the ninth, the chance to draw
OL,19,Flevel with Justin Rose on -12, but it
OL,20,Fwas a chance missed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776272751
OL,3,CInside the club which helped send Rory
OL,4,Con path to greatness
OL,6,FUp to this point, cheering and sighing
OL,7,Fwere heard in equal measure.
OL,9,FBut it was on the back nine when
OL,10,Fcheering began to outweigh all else.
OL,12,FThe 200 or so punters at McIlroy's
OL,13,Fhome club began to feel there was even
OL,14,Fmore reason to believe that this was
OL,15,Fgoing to be Rory's year once again.
OL,17,FHe opened up a two-shot lead over his
OL,18,Fnearest rivals.
OL,20,FA birdie on the 13th made that three.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776272751
OL,3,CInside the club which helped send Rory
OL,4,Con path to greatness
OL,6,FDespite it dropping back to two with
OL,7,FScottie Scheffler breathing down
OL,8,FMcIlroy's neck until the last, there
OL,9,Fwas a sense that history was about to
OL,10,Fbe made by the Holywood man for the
OL,11,Fsecond year in a row.
OL,13,FThen the moment came. Could he do it
OL,14,Ffor himself and for Holywood?
OL,16,FThe roof nearly came off this 122-year-
OL,17,Fold golf club when victory was sealed
OL,18,Fat the 18th, sending those watching
OL,19,Finto a frenzy.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
